  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "dJa2VZfibgndtFz7RN0mfwOPvac=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:48.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "Vetra supports collaborative development through remote drives:\n\n- **Without `--remote-drive`**: Creates a local drive in browser local storage (solo development)\n- **With `--remote-drive <url>`**: Connects to a shared remote drive\n\nKey workflows:\n- **Project Owner**: `ph init --remote-drive <url>` -> Create GitHub repo -> Push -> `ph vetra --watch`\n- **Collaborator**: `ph checkout --remote-drive <url>` -> `ph vetra --watch`\n\nThe **preview drive** (created with `--watch` mode) provides a safe testing environment:\n- The main \"Vetra\" drive syncs with the remote and contains stable configuration\n- The \"Vetra Preview\" drive is local-only for testing document models and editors before syncing\n\nRemote drive configuration is stored in `powerhouse.config.json`:\n```json\n\"vetra\": {\n  \"driveId\": \"bai-specifications\",\n  \"driveUrl\": \"https://switchboard.staging.vetra.io/d/bai-specifications\"\n}\n```",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:48.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:48.000Z"
    }
  },
